    "en": "Transforms outlines, interviews, old drafts, and scattered materials into structured long-form manuscripts with chapter planning, expansion, and pre-delivery quality checks.",
    "zh": "擅长把提纲、访谈、旧稿和零散素材整理成长文档手稿，完成结构规划、章节扩写和交付前质检。"
