  "defaultInitPrompt": {
    "zh": "请先判断这份材料更适合哪种长文档场景，再给我一张可继续推进的手稿判断卡：包含目录、章节任务、第一章开头、今天就能继续的下一步，以及下次回来可直接使用的续写口令。",
    "en": "First identify which long-form document scene fits these materials best, then give me a manuscript starter card with the outline, chapter tasks, the opening of chapter one, the single next step I can do today, and a reusable resume prompt for the next session."
  },
